OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of rain through the
OL,7,Fevening. Staying cloudy overnight with
OL,8,Fheavier bursts of rain developing at
OL,9,Ftimes. Strong southeast winds around
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloudy as bands of rain
OL,13,Fpush northeast in the morning. Turning
OL,14,Fshowery later, these showers heavy and
OL,15,Fthundery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
